Subject: Re: [T2] More balancing

Shop manuals often instruct you to mark the position of the clutch on
the flywheel so you put them back together the same way, but do you
really think the engines are balanced at the factory? I don't have
direct knowledge, but I don't see the assembly line stopping for this.
I think the clutches and flywheels are individually balanced when
manufactured, but not balanced as a rotating mass.

John

